attributes.Long form description: The student is taking apart a shelf. He unscrews the screws from the top shelf first to disassemble the top tray, then removes the legs accordingly.

attributes.Transcription: Well, now disassemble this small shelf from IKEA. So please go ahead.

attributes.Action sentence: The student unscrews the hex socket heads attached to the upper tray and disassembles the tray.

attributes.Incorrect Action Explanation: Student should not drop the hex socket head.

attributes.Action sentence: The student disassembles the first leg of the shelf.

attributes.Incorrect Action Explanation: Student should not drop the hex socket head.

attributes.Action sentence: The student disassembles the second leg of the shelf.
The student disassembles the third leg of the shelf.

attributes.Incorrect Action Explanation: Student should not drop the hex socket head.

attributes.Action sentence: The student disassembles the fourth leg of the shelf and finish disassembling.
